      {
        "id": "01f0d4f86eb9105294d03dd35bceee3e",
        "content": [
          "`main`.`bi_output`.`vg_positionsvolumeandattributes_lc4_source` aggregation rule:\r\n",
          "`main`.`bi_output`.`vg_positionsvolumeandattributes_lc4_source` rows are aggregated and may represent multiple positions.\r\n",
          "When asked “how many positions”, always use\r\n",
          "SUM(num_positions_total) (or SUM(num_positions_lc) for LC).\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\"TP positions\" means total_positions minus lc_positions.\r\n",
          "Whenever the user asks for TP positions, calculate:\r\n",
          "TP_positions = total_positions - lc_positions\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Eligible customer definition (main.bi_output.vg_acquisitionfunnel_em1):\r\n",
          "A customer is considered eligible if all of the following are true:\r\n",
          "IsValidForFunnel = 1 and IsVerifiedFTD = 1 and IsVerifiedFTDPlus2Weeks = 1.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "EM1 (acquisition funnel) attributes represent the customer’s current state only (as of today).\r\n",
          "They are not time-aligned with position events and do not describe the customer’s state at the time a position was opened or closed.\r\n",
          "Use EM1 only for customer segmentation and filtering, not for totals, sums, trend analysis, or causal / before-after conclusions.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "AccountSubProgram and AccountSubProgramID relate only to the eMoney account.\r\n",
          "They are relevant only for customers who have an eMoney account.\r\n",
          "For customers without an eMoney account, these fields are expected to be NULL and this has no analytical meaning.\r\n",
          "Use AccountSubProgram / AccountSubProgramID only when analyzing or aggregating eMoney customers, and do not use them for analyses that include non-eMoney customers.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "Use the following full country list in all analyses whenever country filters or \r\n",
          "country classifications are needed:\r\n",
          "Australia, Indonesia, Liechtenstein, Jersey Island, South Korea, Guadeloupe,\r\n",
          "French Guiana, Bermuda, Denmark, Switzerland, Hong Kong, Saint Martin, Peru,\r\n",
          "Reunion Island, Jordan, Maldives, Paraguay, Kazakhstan, Isle Of Man, Kenya,\r\n",
          "Israel, Armenia, Morocco, Austria, Bulgaria, Dominican Republic, India,\r\n",
