        "question": [
          "For the United Kingdom, consider only customers whose club is NOT Bronze.\n",
          ": \n",
          "\n",
          "This funnel is customer-based, not event-based.\n",
          "Start with all Active TP MIMO customers (this is the base = 100%).\n",
          "From those customers, keep only those who have an eMoney account.\n",
          "From that smaller group, keep only those who are FMI.\n",
